  + [search_phrase_set] is local_ai_manager_primary, lightweight_sop_context_stream, direct_endpoint_role, handoff_threshold, allowance_goal, OpenAI Codex worker on demand, routine manager spend
  + [depth_hint] is impact
  + [coverage_status] is seed
  + [outside] is OpenAI routine-manager spend, direct local mutation, credentials, hidden daemon, destructive action, unbounded spend, and exact hidden state

(narrative_subject_file_table) :subject_key: /file_interest_set and relation_reason/ |unindexed_subject|
  + [subject_key] is the normalized narrative handle
  + [file_interest_set] is local SOP files worth opening first
  + [relation_reason] is why those files matter for the narrated subject
  |unindexed_subject| missing subject entry, stale path, weak relation, unsupported authority, and exhaustive coverage claim
